com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.kit.editor.panel.hierarchy

Class HierarchyDNDController

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.kit.editor.panel.hierarchy.HierarchyDNDController

  • public class HierarchyDNDController
extends java.lang.Object
    Controller for all drag and drop gestures in hierarchy panel. This class does not depend on the TreeView or TreeTableView control and handles only TreeItems.
